<!-- How it works -->
<section class="section comm-how">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:48px;">
      <h2>From first tee to final settlement.</h2>
      <p style="max-width:440px; margin-inline:auto; margin-top:12px;">Five steps. The whole round.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="comm-how__steps">

      <div class="comm-step">
        <div class="comm-step__num" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
        <div class="comm-step__content">
          <h3>Create an event</h3>
          <p>Search for the course from Marker's USGA course database, name the event, and set the date. Optionally attach it to a season series to track cumulative standings over multiple rounds.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-step">
        <div class="comm-step__num" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
        <div class="comm-step__content">
          <h3>Add players</h3>
          <p>Share a link and your group joins from any device — iPhone, Android, or web browser. No app download or account required for players to participate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-step">
        <div class="comm-step__num" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
        <div class="comm-step__content">
          <h3>Build groups</h3>
          <p>Create a scorecard for each cart group, assign players, and set tees. Multiple groups play simultaneously — everyone shares the same live leaderboard across the whole field.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-step">
        <div class="comm-step__num" aria-hidden="true">4</div>
        <div class="comm-step__content">
          <h3>Add games</h3>
          <p>Choose from 11 built-in formats — Skins, Nassau, Wolf, Stableford, and more. Configure handicap, select which players are in, and set stakes. Marker handles all the math from there.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-step">
        <div class="comm-step__num" aria-hidden="true">5</div>
        <div class="comm-step__content">
          <h3>Score live and settle</h3>
          <p>Every player enters scores on their own device. The leaderboard updates hole by hole. Lock the event when the round ends and Marker shows exactly who owes who — across every game, in one screen.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Features -->
<section class="section section--white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:48px;">
      <h2>Everything you need to run the event.</h2>
      <p style="max-width:500px; margin-inline:auto; margin-top:12px;">Built for the commissioner who wants full control without the administrative overhead.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="comm-features-grid">

      <div class="comm-feature-card">
        <div class="comm-feature-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Live Leaderboard for the Field</h3>
        <p>Every player's phone shows real-time standings across all groups as scores come in hole by hole. No waiting for carts to return — everyone knows where they stand.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-feature-card">
        <div class="comm-feature-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="4" y1="21" x2="4" y2="14"/><line x1="4" y1="10" x2="4" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="20" y1="21" x2="20" y2="16"/><line x1="20" y1="12" x2="20" y2="3"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="7" y2="14"/><line x1="9" y1="8" x2="15" y2="8"/><line x1="17" y1="16" x2="23" y2="16"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>USGA Handicap Management</h3>
        <p>Marker is an Official USGA Handicap Data Affiliate. Course handicaps calculate from current indexes automatically. Allowances, stroke overrides, and World Handicap System rules are all built in.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-feature-card">
        <div class="comm-feature-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Multiple Games, One Event</h3>
        <p>Add Skins, Nassau, and Wolf to the same event. Each game tracks independently — different players, different stakes, different formats — and settles separately when the round ends.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-feature-card">
        <div class="comm-feature-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Season Series</h3>
        <p>Group your events into a series and track cumulative standings across the whole season. Results from each event roll up automatically. Series management is a commissioner feature.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-feature-card">
        <div class="comm-feature-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Automatic Settlement</h3>
        <p>Lock the event when the round ends and Marker calculates exactly who owes who across every game. No mental math, no disputes, no waiting until someone gets home to run the numbers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-feature-card">
        <div class="comm-feature-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="m21.64 3.64-1.28-1.28a1.21 1.21 0 0 0-1.72 0L2.36 18.64a1.21 1.21 0 0 0 0 1.72l1.28 1.28a1.2 1.2 0 0 0 1.72 0L21.64 5.36a1.2 1.2 0 0 0 0-1.72z"/><path d="m14 7 3 3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>AI Game Generation</h3>
        <p>Describe a custom format in plain English and Marker generates the scoring rules. Review before activating. Useful for group-specific house formats that don't fit a standard built-in game.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Games commissioners run -->
<section class="section comm-games">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="comm-games__header">
      <h2>Formats your group already plays.</h2>
      <p>Every game is built in — no configuration required to add it. Pick the format, set stakes, and play.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="comm-games__grid">

      <a href="{{ '/games/wolf/' | url }}" class="comm-game-card">
        <h3>Wolf</h3>
        <p>Rotating lone wolf. Every hole, the wolf picks their team — or goes it alone for double stakes. Premium.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="{{ '/games/nassau/' | url }}" class="comm-game-card">
        <h3>Nassau</h3>
        <p>Three separate bets: front 9, back 9, and full 18. Optional press rules built in.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="{{ '/games/skins/' | url }}" class="comm-game-card">
        <h3>Skins</h3>
        <p>Win the hole outright or the pot carries. Marker tracks every skin and shows the live payout.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="{{ '/games/match-play/' | url }}" class="comm-game-card">
        <h3>Match Play</h3>
        <p>Head-to-head, hole by hole. Marker tracks standing (2UP, 3DOWN) and closes the match automatically.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="{{ '/games/stableford/' | url }}" class="comm-game-card">
        <h3>Stableford</h3>
        <p>Points relative to par. Works well for mixed-handicap groups where scoring gaps are wide.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="{{ '/games/team-count-x/' | url }}" class="comm-game-card">
        <h3>TeamCountX</h3>
        <p>Team stroke play where each team selects X scores per hole. Scales to any team size. Premium.</p>
      </a>

    </div>
    <p class="comm-games__all"><a href="{{ '/games/' | url }}">Browse all 11 game formats →</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Trust stats -->
<section class="section section--white">
  <div class="container">
    {{ TrustStats() }}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Pricing -->
<section class="section pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pricing__header">
      <h2>Start free. Upgrade when you need more.</h2>
      <p>Your first 3 events are included — no credit card, no time limit. Premium unlocks Wolf, TeamCountX, and season series.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing__grid">
      {% for plan in pricing.plans %}
      <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--{{ plan.id }}">
        <p class="pricing-card__plan">{{ plan.name }}</p>
        <div class="pricing-card__price">
          <span class="pricing-card__amount">{{ plan.amount }}</span>
          {% if plan.period %}<span class="pricing-card__period">{{ plan.period }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <p class="pricing-card__alt">{{ plan.altText }}</p>
        <div class="pricing-card__divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <ul class="pricing-card__features">
          {% for feature in plan.features %}
          <li>{{ feature }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% if plan.cta %}
        <a href="{{ plan.cta.href }}" class="btn btn-ghost">{{ plan.cta.text }}</a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA band -->
<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Start your first event in under a minute.</h2>
    <p>No spreadsheets. No group texts. No arguments at the 19th hole.</p>
    <div class="cta-band__actions">
      <a href="https://app.marker.golf" class="btn btn-primary">Start Your First Event</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
